2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper discusses the use of probabilistic maps and the development of better segmentation methods, which are related to machine learning. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper deals with the evaluation of segmentation algorithms, which is a common topic in artificial intelligence. 
4. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) - The paper discusses the use of deep-brain stimulation and automatic segmentation of the subthalamic-nucleus, which are related to neural computing. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with image segmentation and evaluation, which are related to multimedia.
